# Testing Rules — Omnix Runtime

Source: `packages/core/standards/testing.md`

- Unit: fast, no IO, no framework. Test behavior, not implementation.
- Integration: real DB/queue in container.
- E2E: critical flows only, single-digit count.
- One reason to fail per test.
- Every bug fix gets a regression test.
- No shared mutable state between tests.
- Flaky tests are bugs — quarantine, fix, or delete. Never retry-until-green.
- Mock at boundaries (HTTP, time, randomness). Don't mock the thing under test.
